{"tid":1722003,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"希望下星期二嗰場多啲人入場睇港隊","createTime":"2019-11-14T20:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T12:06:00.000Z","uid":64656,"like":69,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a72d259d410c8f24ab893f4afe772d701c86e59f","tid":1722003,"uid":64656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:50:03.000Z","msg":"一齊唱榮光 又可以分散警力<br />\n今日喺東華嗰邊入 勁多狗<br />\n東華停車場+隔嚟間中學<br />\n4000人都擺咁多人 坐爆肯定擺更多<br />\n仲唔怕冇車 安排巴士你走人<br />\n<br />\n【體路專訊】香港足球代表隊今晚（14日）力戰賽和巴林，搶得世界盃外圍賽次圈第2分。賽後獲選為最有價值球員的港足門將葉鴻輝及中場陳俊樂均認為，球隊在控球及轉守為攻的能力比以往數場提升不少，前者同時希望今場比賽能帶給市民正能量。"},{"pid":"129ec04822d7c7705db44c2f651e4d28033e07a2","tid":1722003,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"[光復香港 時代革命] 2022世盃外 香港 對 柬埔寨 19/11 20:00 即場討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720936</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"62b0af74bc9a37f7949657c864275c12d3e2a173","tid":1722003,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:41:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d730c27ca92b8bbac92f5f7443b8108b0b4e7b20","tid":1722003,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"下星期二 11月19號 香港主場對柬埔寨冇人講？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725007</a>"},{"pid":"6322718e1fbd0aebbbe63e85746a9f8fb212a147","tid":1722003,"uid":4957,"like":4,"dislike":61,"score":-57,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:48.000Z","msg":"咁既波 免費都唔會睇 浪費時間"},{"pid":"daea53d5da6c53c2a301f48ff5d347a617eead54","tid":1722003,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2bbd0d813820f232d7fe6072c21f0abbe6a9639b","tid":1722003,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T23:26:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d16cfc842acce96bf1f42107552eb12541e76